Properties.Name: Имя фильтра
Properties.RowSource: Select [@QueriesFilters].[Name] As [Имя фильтра], [@QueriesFilters].[ID] From [@QueriesFilters] Inner Join [@Forms] On ([@QueriesFilters].[QueryID]=[@Forms].[QueryID]) Where [@Forms].[Name]='|0' Order by [@QueriesFilters].[Name];

Properties.Name: Имя настройки
Properties.RowSource: Select [@FormsTuning].[Name] As [Имя настройки], [@FormsTuning].[ID] From [@FormsTuning] Inner Join [@Forms] On ([@FormsTuning].[FormID]=[@Forms].[ID]) Where [@Forms].[Name]='|0' Order by [@FormsTuning].[Name];
